SYNQDRIVE MASTER PROJECT CONTEXT

Product: SynqDrive
Type: Multi‑tenant SaaS platform for mobility and vehicle operations.

Main product modules:
- Rental Solution
- Fleet Solution
- Taxi Dispatch

Platform goals:
Provide companies with operational control, vehicle visibility,
service intelligence, automation and integrations.

------------------------------------------------
MULTI‑TENANT MODEL
------------------------------------------------
Organizations are tenants.
Each organization has isolated data.

Platform structure:

Platform (Master Admin)
 └ Organizations
     └ Users
     └ Stations
     └ Vehicles
     └ Customers
     └ Bookings
     └ Integrations
     └ Billing

Tenant isolation must always be enforced.

------------------------------------------------
CORE ROLES
------------------------------------------------
Master Admin
Org Admin
Sub Admin
Worker
Driver
Customer

Master Admin controls:
- organizations
- platform settings
- product licensing
- billing overview
- prospects database
- integrations (DIMO, Stripe)

------------------------------------------------
PRODUCT LICENSING
------------------------------------------------
Organizations may enable products:

- Rental Solution
- Fleet Solution
- Taxi Dispatch

Enabled products determine:
- available modules
- permissions
- billing

------------------------------------------------
DIMO VEHICLE SOURCE
------------------------------------------------
Vehicles originate from DIMO telemetry.

DIMO provides:
VIN
Make
Model
Year
Fuel Type

These are trusted identity fields.

Vehicles appear first as:

Non Registered Vehicles (mirrored from DIMO)

Then they can be registered into SynqDrive
and assigned to an organization.

------------------------------------------------
VEHICLE INTELLIGENCE MODEL
------------------------------------------------

SynqDrive stores reference data needed for
estimating component condition.

Domains:

Battery reference data
Tire setups and tread measurements
Brake reference specifications
Service events

These combine with telematics data
to estimate vehicle health later.

------------------------------------------------
INTEGRATIONS
------------------------------------------------

Platform level integrations:
- DIMO
- Stripe

Organization level integrations:
- WooCommerce
- Shopify

Purpose:
sync bookings
sync payments
external website integration

------------------------------------------------
PROSPECT DATABASE
------------------------------------------------

Master Admin maintains a database of potential partners:

Taxi companies
Rental companies
Fleet operators
Logistics companies

Prospects may later convert into organizations.

------------------------------------------------
INTERNATIONALIZATION
------------------------------------------------

SynqDrive must support multiple languages:

English
German
French
Dutch
Spanish
Italian
Polish
Czech

All UI text should use translation keys.

------------------------------------------------
TECH STACK DIRECTION
------------------------------------------------

Frontend:
Next.js

Backend:
NestJS

Database:
PostgreSQL

ORM:
Prisma

Workers:
Redis + BullMQ

Architecture:
Modular monolith

------------------------------------------------
SOURCE OF TRUTH
------------------------------------------------

Figma defines UI layout.

Backend must implement behavior behind it.